{"tid":1924010,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"\"雖然係香港人做出嚟,但要貼上中國製造\"     理大快速測試機 香港零資助 深圳政府招手","createTime":"2020-03-13T11:55:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T15:07:21.000Z","uid":28202,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"2cfceca6af4af3382fb2f396ea44ecae8570e096","tid":1924010,"uid":28202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:55:33.000Z","msg":"此話一出,之後有香港人捐款,<br />\n但唔知之後會唔會都係去深圳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新聞刺針<br />\n&middot; Follow<br />\nToday at 12:15 &middot;<br />\n理大快速測試機 零資助之謎<br />\n【理大快速測試機 $0 資助之謎】<br />\n<br />\n理工大學早前研發出一部「快速測試機」，一小時可檢測到新型肺炎、沙士等40種病毒及細菌，計劃得到袁國勇、馬化騰支持，但他們向創科署申請資金時，連面試機會都沒有，就被拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n《新聞刺針》拆解理大快速測試機零資助之謎。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1523535567810403\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D1523535567810403&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7j3psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=2f0cb7b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1523535567810403</a><br />\n<br />\n【專訪】理大研發武漢肺炎快速診斷儀 劉樂庭：政府零資助 + 全香港人團隊<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9fM__sGVidE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9fM__sGVidE&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7j3psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=b0b1cbb9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9fM__sGVidE</a>"},{"pid":"5d62d15594258ec008842a635aaeda43b44b1543","tid":1924010,"uid":132128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:56:48.000Z","msg":"我地係咪唔可以用支那野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f28e2ded713c1d9379f5891c76f03c3ca5c28a3","tid":1924010,"uid":205469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T11:57:38.000Z","msg":"眾籌啦"},{"pid":"89910d8823b5849b15391b1405b71036717a7ab0","tid":1924010,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited